# Mission: Design docs for C7 (Git viewer) + C8 (External editor integration)

You are an autonomous agent working in git worktree `design+c7-c8-viewer-editor` (branch `worktree-design+c7-c8-viewer-editor`). The user is asleep — make your best-judgement decisions and document them.

## Your deliverables

Two design documents:

1. **`docs/design-docs/c7-git-viewer.md`** (~300–500 lines)
2. **`docs/design-docs/c8-editor-integration.md`** (~200–400 lines — simpler than others)

Placeholders exist — overwrite them.

